NAME
	files_modified - XXX

SYNOPSIS
	mixed *files_modified(string str, int hours, int maxsz, int dir)

DESCRIPTION
	This is available only if the mud is configured to use the 
	FILES_MODIFIED LPC extension.

	XXX

	You can find the extension on github here:
	https://github.com/november-kilo/dgd-lpc-ext

RETURN VALUE
	If the extension is disabled it will return nil.

EXAMPLES
	XXX

SEE ALSO
	afun/blogit, afun/files_modified, afun/sqlite3_exec,
	afun/sqlite3_select
